body:
Versus is a relatively new skin line in League, but the event already carries a lot of weight. Two rival champions are given legendary skins in a universe which pits them against one another as opposing godlike figures of order and chaos. While it may seem black and white on surface level, both figures will have their pros and cons. Yasuo and Riven seem to lean toward the &quot;both options are good, in their way&quot; angle, while Garen and Darius seem to lean toward both of them being evil, in their way. The event itself also asks players to pick a side, so that we, the players, &quot;decide&quot; who wins the ultimate conflict in the end, even though those outcomes don&#039;t seem to be canon. Regardless, with the success of the first two Versus events, people seem to be looking forward to the next ones eagerly. 

These are some rivalries that I would love to see get Versus skins, and they&#039;re the ones that I could see being the most likely to have the event in the future.

