Both have been with a high fantasy theme so far, I would like to give some emphasis on the steampunk thematics of the game next time.
Instead of seeing 2 god kings fighting each other in a medieval battlefield, I would like 2 cities with high technology fight each other.

Law VS Anarchy, one thinks that Progress is just achievable by giving everyone clear rules to follow. The other thinks that we have to embrace chaos and should let everyone study every field they want to (even "morally evil" fields) as they please to advance.

